<title type="html"><![CDATA[6/26(Sat.)How our views on work have changed forever/Can We Stop the Spread of Misinformation?(Kelvin)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=510&amp;p=532#p532"><![CDATA[
6/26(Sat.)How our views on work have changed forever/Can We Stop the Spread of Misinformation?(Kelvin)<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">There is no on-site meeting during the pandemic of COVID-19.<br /><br /><br />加入 Zoom 會議<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... NKSU5MQT09<br /><br />會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233<br /><br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br />At the presentation the time limit is 1-2 minutes for each speaker.</span><br /><br /><br />Article1:<br />How our views on work have changed forever<br /><a href="https://www.bbc.com/worklife/article/20201209-how-our-views-on-work-have-changed-forever" class="postlink">https://www.bbc.com/worklife/article/20201209-how-our-views-on-work-have-changed-forever</a><br />1:Which work  style do you prefer?work at home or work with colleagues?<br />2:If you could start over,Will you change your career ?<br />3:For some people money is the most important thing forb them to go to work ,but the others they want to find value in their career,What's your definition of your career?<br /><br />Article2:<br />Can We Stop the Spread of Misinformation?<br /><a href="http://www.psychologytoday.com/intl/blog/mental-mishaps/201907/can-we-stop-the-spread-misinformation" class="postlink">http://www.psychologytoday.com/intl/blog/mental-mishaps/201907/can-we-stop-the-spread-misinformation</a><br />1:How often do you encounter misinformation or news?<br />2:Each of us may be the unwitting agent,What can you do for yourself to be a witting agent ?<br />3:Personal information security is important,Have you ever experienced international fraud or Phone Scams?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Tue Jun 22, 2021 1:31 am</p><hr />
